categories: Category:Jedi Masters of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: Tre Timbal was a Jedi Master who served the Jedi Order and the Galactic Republic during the Cold War against the resurgent Sith Empire. Timbal, Kirbi, Luquena, and another Jedi attempted to investigate a rakghoul warren on Taris, but they were killed by nekghouls.
